The paper also discusses optimization algorithms and convex optimization, which suggests cs.NA (Numerical Analysis) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) as possible categories. Finally, the paper deals with computational methods and algorithms, which suggests cs.SI (Systems and Control) as a possible category.
